<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-6359] sstableloader does not free off-heap memory for index summary</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6359</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Although sstableloader tells &lt;tt&gt;SSTableReaders&lt;/tt&gt; to release their references to the &lt;tt&gt;IndexSummary&lt;/tt&gt; objects, the summary&apos;s &lt;tt&gt;Memory&lt;/tt&gt; is never &lt;tt&gt;free()&lt;/tt&gt;&apos;d, causing an off-heap memory leak.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12679499">CASSANDRA-6359</key>
            <summary>sstableloader does not free off-heap memory for index summary</summary>
